According to the latest statistics released by the Mpumalanga Department of Health, the number of positive cases are as follows: Steve Tshwete – 1759 positive cases, 1339 recoveries, 5 fatalities. eMalahleni – 4214 positive cases, 3433 recoveries, 23 fatalities. Govan Mbeki – 2652 positive cases, 1958 recoveries, 22 fatalities. Mbombela – 2833 positive cases, 1933 recoveries, 10 fatalities. •According to the Department of Health, only five Covid-19 related deaths have been reported for the Steve Tshwete district. It can, however, be confirmed, that 10 Middelburg residents have since passed away due to Covid-19.